<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id146b9a56-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s379dd–1"><num value="379dd–1">§ 379dd–1.</num><heading> Location of Foundation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Foundation shall, if practicable, be located not more than 20 miles from the District of Columbia.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id146b9a57-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d">(<ref href="/us/act/1938-06-25/ch675/s771">June 25, 1938, ch. 675, § 771</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/110/85/tVI/s601/b">Pub. L. 110–85, title VI, § 601(b)</ref>, <date date="2007-09-27">Sept. 27, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/121/897">121 Stat. 897</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
